Hei, Vaijayanti.

00:07:16.105 --> 00:07:18.267
Tidak perlu terlalu bahagia.

00:07:19.484 --> 00:07:21.336
Walaupun dia temanmu...

00:07:22.511 --> 00:07:26.538
...tapi dia hendak
menyebut nama Bondita.

00:07:27.471 --> 00:07:28.863
