00:07:29.444 --> 00:07:31.485
...teman tidak menertawakanmu.

00:07:32.431 --> 00:07:34.958
Dia merindukan Bondita.

00:07:37.458 --> 00:07:39.093
'Bondita!'

00:07:40.850 --> 00:07:44.107
