00:16:37.985 --> 00:16:39.357
Apa...

00:16:41.270 --> 00:16:42.698
Vaijayanti...

00:16:43.270 --> 00:16:44.842
Aku ingin tahu...

00:16:45.310 --> 00:16:49.300
